    "credits": "3",
    "description": "This course invites you on a creative journey to redefine sustainable design in architecture through an immersive learning experience. \"Eco-Design\"empowers you to think critically about ecological principles and apply them with advanced diagramming and visual storytelling, using a blend of manual, digital, and AI-driven techniques. You'll dive into the synergy between hand-drawn sketches, digital illustrations, and AI-generated visuals to communicate complex sustainable concepts effectively. Through hands-on projects and collaborative workshops, you'll develop skills in generative design drawing and learn to communicate ideas that inspire ecological innovation and thoughtful technology use. With a strong foundation in digital and AI tools, you'll transform ideas into visually compelling forms and narratives."
