    "name": "Independent Study in Design Thinking",
    "credits": "1",
    "description": "Graduate students apply design thinking and/or lean startup concepts to a real-world project. This course requires a high degree of self-direction in all aspects of the project including defining specificmilestones and deliverables. There will be regular coaching froman Academy for Innovation and Entrepreneurship team member. Restriction:Permission required by the Academy for Innovation and Entreurship"
