    "description": "Introduces students to special relativity and quantum mechanics. Topics include relativistic spacetime and 4-momentum, historical origins of quantum mechanics, single particle bound states and scattering in one dimension, the hydrogen atom, spin-1/2, and quantum information theory. Students completing PHYS400 will gain proficiency in Modern Physics (PHYS371) and Quantum Physics 1 (PHYS401)."
